01:06:41.427 --> 01:06:42.487
Hello.

01:06:43.557 --> 01:06:44.657
Yu Bin, can I have a moment with you?

01:06:45.757 --> 01:06:47.666
- Can you stir it once? - I'll keep an eye on it.

01:06:47.667 --> 01:06:50.196
