01:06:50.197 --> 01:06:52.696
- That's it! - He called Yu Bin.

01:06:52.697 --> 01:06:54.466
That's it!

01:06:54.467 --> 01:06:56.766
- That's my son. - He's so straightforward.

01:06:56.767 --> 01:06:59.106
Nice. That's how a man should be.

01:06:59.107 --> 01:07:00.306
- That's cheating. - Yes.

01:07:00.307 --> 01:07:01.507
- A man... - He's disqualified.

01:07:05.847 --> 01:07:07.647
- Yes? What... - Please go inside.

01:07:09.247 --> 01:07:11.356
Me? Why...

01:07:11.357 --> 01:07:12.587
Why am I in here?

01:07:13.787 --> 01:07:15.557
- So nobody can snatch you away. - I see.

01:07:15.727 --> 01:07:17.756
- "So nobody can snatch you away." - "So nobody can snatch you away."

01:07:17.757 --> 01:07:20.126
(What he said makes her dad happy.)

01:07:20.127 --> 01:07:21.366
That's it!

01:07:21.367 --> 01:07:23.197
- That's cheating! - What a nice thing to say.

01:07:23.327 --> 01:07:25.466
Women are deeply moved...

01:07:25.467 --> 01:07:28.837
- when they hear stuff like this. - Of course.

01:07:29.007 --> 01:07:31.907
- Yu Bin is moved now. - Yes, she is.

01:07:35.847 --> 01:07:38.776
(In a rush, he wears Jae Hyuk's jacket.)

01:07:38.777 --> 01:07:39.917
- Jae Hyuk's jacket? - What?

01:07:40.317 --> 01:07:41.517
What is he doing?

01:07:41.687 --> 01:07:43.717
- It isn't even his. - What is he doing?

01:07:44.287 --> 01:07:46.157
(Knocking)

01:07:50.527 --> 01:07:52.097
- Hello. - Hello.

01:07:52.627 --> 01:07:55.327
They're my presents for you.

01:07:55.867 --> 01:07:57.667
My gosh.

01:07:57.767 --> 01:07:58.797
What are these for?

01:07:59.567 --> 01:08:00.736
Go on a date with me.

01:08:00.737 --> 01:08:02.336
Really? Sure.

01:08:02.337 --> 01:08:03.436
Go on a date with me.

01:08:03.437 --> 01:08:05.607
Really? Sure, I'd like that.

01:08:05.837 --> 01:08:06.977
Nobody asked you out yet, right?

01:08:07.437 --> 01:08:08.447
No.

01:08:08.747 --> 01:08:10.246
- Is this first-come first-served? - That's right.

01:08:10.247 --> 01:08:12.816
- I see. Thank you. - No problem.

01:08:12.817 --> 01:08:15.117
(Yu Bin is the first to be asked out by Yoon Hoo.)

01:08:16.687 --> 01:08:20.787
The presents would keep me warm during the date,

01:08:20.857 --> 01:08:22.057
so I liked it.

01:08:22.327 --> 01:08:23.627
I felt very good.

01:08:23.727 --> 01:08:25.997
She must be on cloud nine.

01:08:26.397 --> 01:08:29.366
(Those left now are Hee Dong, Jae Seung,)

01:08:29.367 --> 01:08:31.767
(and Jae Hyuk.)

01:08:32.497 --> 01:08:34.266
- I think it's almost done. - Yes.

01:08:34.267 --> 01:08:35.307
(Eun Byul and Si Woo are waiting for the guys to ask them out.)

01:08:37.437 --> 01:08:38.936
This is bad.

01:08:38.937 --> 01:08:41.407
We should be saying that. This is bad.

01:08:42.677 --> 01:08:45.677
(Checking his face)

01:08:47.247 --> 01:08:52.057
(After looking in the mirror, Jae Seung finally gets going.)

01:08:52.887 --> 01:08:56.457
I have one person in mind.

01:09:00.827 --> 01:09:02.426
Excuse me, Si Woo. Could I...

01:09:02.427 --> 01:09:03.966
- speak with you for a moment? - Okay.

01:09:03.967 --> 01:09:07.907
(The girl on Jae Seung's mind is Si Woo.)

01:09:09.167 --> 01:09:10.537
Si Woo.

01:09:11.377 --> 01:09:13.207
He's ever so consistent.

01:09:13.837 --> 01:09:15.576
He wavered for a moment,

01:09:15.577 --> 01:09:17.577
but he went back to being consistent.

01:09:18.117 --> 01:09:19.217
(Wiping his nose)

01:09:19.877 --> 01:09:21.887
- Please wait for a while. - Okay.

01:09:26.157 --> 01:09:29.287
(He takes the poetry book with a fluttering heart.)

01:09:29.557 --> 01:09:30.587
Well...

01:09:31.657 --> 01:09:35.367
I'd like to ask you out on a date.

01:09:35.727 --> 01:09:37.166
- Here. - Thank you.

01:09:37.167 --> 01:09:39.767
(Jae Seung asks Si Woo out as he gives her the poetry book.)

01:09:40.537 --> 01:09:43.937
(Feeling embarrassed, he runs away quickly.)

01:09:44.407 --> 01:09:47.077
(Did you like Jae Seung's present?)

01:09:47.277 --> 01:09:49.876
Jae Seung came to me first...

01:09:49.877 --> 01:09:51.476
and gave me...

01:09:51.477 --> 01:09:53.847
a collection of poems.

01:09:54.217 --> 01:09:57.186
- Will she like it? - Does Si Woo like poetry?

01:09:57.187 --> 01:09:58.317
Does she like it?

01:09:58.817 --> 01:10:02.486
I really like the poem "Grass Flower..."

01:10:02.487 --> 01:10:04.256
and I read it often.

01:10:04.257 --> 01:10:08.297
I thought, "Is this coincidence?"

01:10:09.667 --> 01:10:11.367
His dad chose it.

01:10:11.767 --> 01:10:13.766
- And it worked. - She likes it.

01:10:13.767 --> 01:10:15.737
(The poetry book captures Si Woo's heart.)

01:10:16.137 --> 01:10:17.206
(Why did you ask Si Woo out on a date?)

01:10:17.207 --> 01:10:20.636
I remember asking her...

01:10:20.637 --> 01:10:23.177
if she would be okay with going on a date with me.

01:10:23.507 --> 01:10:25.477
(During their first meeting)

01:10:25.677 --> 01:10:27.477
I like taking pictures.

01:10:27.817 --> 01:10:31.857
(They both like taking pictures.)

01:10:32.587 --> 01:10:33.957
During the Attraction Selection,

01:10:34.527 --> 01:10:36.086
I think the message I got was,

01:10:36.087 --> 01:10:38.557
"Let's go to a scenic spot and take pictures together."

01:10:38.727 --> 01:10:40.857
I thought that was from Si Woo.

01:10:41.127 --> 01:10:42.666
It'd be nice to go on a date with her...

01:10:42.667 --> 01:10:44.196
to a place with a nice view.

01:10:44.197 --> 01:10:46.937
That's why he asked Si Woo out.

01:10:47.637 --> 01:10:50.137
But Eun Byul sent that text.

01:10:51.237 --> 01:10:52.906
The date will be tough.

01:10:52.907 --> 01:10:54.177
He thought long and hard.

01:10:54.337 --> 01:10:57.106
I think Jae Seung is a fool.

01:10:57.107 --> 01:10:58.777
He's so dense.

01:10:59.147 --> 01:11:01.086
- That can't be true. - He's so dense.

01:11:01.087 --> 01:11:03.087
He's unaware of my daughter's feelings.

01:11:03.647 --> 01:11:06.157
- The date will be rough. - Why?

01:11:06.317 --> 01:11:09.556
Jae Seung thinks Si Woo sent him the text.

01:11:09.557 --> 01:11:11.596
- Yes. - But once the truth comes out...

01:11:11.597 --> 01:11:12.627
Yes.

01:11:12.797 --> 01:11:13.956
It'll be...

01:11:13.957 --> 01:11:15.966
They can become closer before they find out the truth.

01:11:15.967 --> 01:11:17.837
- Yes. - You never know how it'll turn out.

01:11:17.967 --> 01:11:22.007
(Meanwhile, Eun Byul is left alone in the kitchen.)

01:11:22.467 --> 01:11:26.577
I voted for Jae Seung.

01:11:26.807 --> 01:11:29.006
So I hoped...

01:11:29.007 --> 01:11:32.746
to go on a 1-on-1 date with Jae Seung.

01:11:32.747 --> 01:11:33.977
Oh, dear.

01:11:34.017 --> 01:11:36.117
(Upset)

01:11:38.787 --> 01:11:41.257
It's a pity,

01:11:41.687 --> 01:11:44.957
but I think I have a lot of opportunities to talk with him.

01:11:48.097 --> 01:11:49.227
Did you ask someone out?

01:11:49.467 --> 01:11:50.666
- I did. - You did?

01:11:50.667 --> 01:11:52.467
- I'll go now. - Do your best.

01:11:53.297 --> 01:11:55.636
Are we supposed to go one by one...

01:11:55.637 --> 01:11:57.207
when it's first-come first-served?

01:11:58.777 --> 01:12:00.636
Shouldn't we fight to go first?

01:12:00.637 --> 01:12:02.077
- That's right. - That's right.

01:12:03.047 --> 01:12:04.347
I should go, but...

01:12:05.677 --> 01:12:07.346
- Did you ask someone out? - Yes.

01:12:07.347 --> 01:12:08.917
- You did? - Yes.

01:12:09.287 --> 01:12:10.887
Really? Then I...

01:12:11.517 --> 01:12:13.516
I didn't know you guys already did.

01:12:13.517 --> 01:12:15.087
- Hee Dong. - You...

01:12:15.427 --> 01:12:18.097
(Meanwhile, Jae Hyuk goes to ask a girl out.)

01:12:18.457 --> 01:12:22.027
I had one person in mind to ask out on a date.

01:12:22.127 --> 01:12:23.467
So I didn't need to think.

01:12:23.927 --> 01:12:27.467
I wanted to ask Si Woo out.

01:12:27.837 --> 01:12:29.766
During the Attraction Selection on the first day,

01:12:29.767 --> 01:12:31.307
I chose Si Woo.

01:12:32.107 --> 01:12:33.306
I want to go on a 1-on-1 date with her...

01:12:33.307 --> 01:12:35.107
and get to know her better.

01:12:35.177 --> 01:12:37.406
- Oh, dear. - He...

01:12:37.407 --> 01:12:38.946
But Si Woo is already chosen, right?

01:12:38.947 --> 01:12:39.976
- She is. - She is.

01:12:39.977 --> 01:12:41.686
What was he doing just now?

01:12:41.687 --> 01:12:42.687
Exactly.

01:12:42.688 --> 01:12:44.516
He should act fast.

01:12:44.517 --> 01:12:45.787
(Feeling bad for him)

01:12:48.787 --> 01:12:50.326
I'll put it here.

01:12:50.327 --> 01:12:51.457
Eggs again?

01:12:51.757 --> 01:12:52.997
- Are you cooking eggs? - I'm boiling eggs.

01:12:57.027 --> 01:12:59.296
Did someone ask you out already?

01:12:59.297 --> 01:13:00.596
- Yes. - Someone did?

01:13:00.597 --> 01:13:01.867
Really?

01:13:02.207 --> 01:13:04.407
Gosh, Jae Hyuk.

01:13:04.637 --> 01:13:06.136
Gosh, you jerk.

01:13:06.137 --> 01:13:08.747
- Jae Hyuk. - Oh, Jae Hyuk.

01:13:08.777 --> 01:13:11.146
Even the extra time is over.

01:13:11.147 --> 01:13:13.117
Jae Hyuk is one step behind.

01:13:13.477 --> 01:13:14.986
I feel bad for him.

01:13:14.987 --> 01:13:16.147
Me too.

01:13:16.687 --> 01:13:17.887
It's too bad.

01:13:18.517 --> 01:13:20.557
Oh, well...

01:13:21.327 --> 01:13:22.886
I see. Have fun.

01:13:22.887 --> 01:13:23.957
Next time...

01:13:30.997 --> 01:13:32.137
I regretted it.

01:13:32.537 --> 01:13:35.537
I should've gone to her room and asked her out.

01:13:35.967 --> 01:13:37.267
I regretted it.

01:13:38.137 --> 01:13:39.906
- Exactly. - Yes.

01:13:39.907 --> 01:13:40.936
- He could've gone. - You should've acted fast.

01:13:40.937 --> 01:13:42.106
He had the chance.

01:13:42.107 --> 01:13:44.006
Why does he always regret belatedly?

01:13:44.007 --> 01:13:45.746
Whose son is he?

01:13:45.747 --> 01:13:46.916
Seriously.

01:13:46.917 --> 01:13:48.417
This is frustrating.

01:13:50.887 --> 01:13:52.287
(Knocking)

01:13:52.587 --> 01:13:53.817
He went to Eun Byul.

01:13:55.827 --> 01:13:56.926
- Hello. - Eun Byul.

01:13:56.927 --> 01:13:58.896
Would you like to go on a date with me today?

01:13:58.897 --> 01:14:00.597
Sure, sounds good.

01:14:00.927 --> 01:14:02.867
And this is my present.

01:14:03.327 --> 01:14:04.466
What is this?

01:14:04.467 --> 01:14:06.536
It's perfume. Do you like perfume?

01:14:06.537 --> 01:14:08.767
Yes, I do.

01:14:10.507 --> 01:14:12.006
- Thank you. - Welcome.

01:14:12.007 --> 01:14:13.576
- See you later. - See you.

01:14:13.577 --> 01:14:14.877
- Bye. - Thank you.

01:14:24.117 --> 01:14:26.617
Jae Hyuk chose me.

01:14:26.857 --> 01:14:29.256
I think I was his second choice.

01:14:29.257 --> 01:14:32.297
- She knows. - I'm sorry, Eun Byul.

01:14:32.527 --> 01:14:34.427
Since she was with them.

01:14:34.767 --> 01:14:36.627
Before he chose me,

01:14:36.767 --> 01:14:39.867
Si Woo was in the kitchen.

01:14:40.137 --> 01:14:42.536
"He must want to ask her out."

01:14:42.537 --> 01:14:44.136
So I left the kitchen...

01:14:44.137 --> 01:14:47.177
for them to talk in private.

01:14:47.277 --> 01:14:49.976
So I thought he's interested in me...

01:14:49.977 --> 01:14:54.017
second to Si Woo.

01:14:55.047 --> 01:14:56.986
- That's sad. - Although...

01:14:56.987 --> 01:14:59.116
I chose Jae Seung,

01:14:59.117 --> 01:15:02.727
I wanted to know more about Jae Hyuk too.

01:15:02.857 --> 01:15:05.027
So I was looking forward to it.

01:15:05.627 --> 01:15:08.067
Thank you, Eun Byul.

01:15:08.867 --> 01:15:10.367
- Thank you. - He's thanking her.

01:15:11.437 --> 01:15:13.237
This breaks my heart.

01:15:13.767 --> 01:15:16.136
I didn't feel this way even when I was on the World Cup.

01:15:16.137 --> 01:15:17.806
- He... - This is hard to watch.

01:15:17.807 --> 01:15:19.337
(Suffering mentally)

01:15:19.577 --> 01:15:20.776
This is so hard.

01:15:20.777 --> 01:15:22.576
This is harder than playing on the World Cup.

01:15:22.577 --> 01:15:25.117
For me, this is harder than giving birth.

01:15:26.077 --> 01:15:28.746
Giving a birth to another baby would be easier.

01:15:28.747 --> 01:15:30.286
- This is so hard to watch. - The mother knows...

01:15:30.287 --> 01:15:32.817
that her daughter was a second choice.

01:15:33.357 --> 01:15:35.356
- Will Hee Dong stay in the dorm? - What about Hee Dong?

01:15:35.357 --> 01:15:36.427
He still...

01:15:38.527 --> 01:15:40.327
- Did you do it? - Yes.

01:15:43.367 --> 01:15:47.797
(Shaking his head)

01:15:48.267 --> 01:15:50.567
- I got a text. - You got a text?

01:15:50.837 --> 01:15:52.877
"All the dates have been matched."

01:15:52.907 --> 01:15:53.977
I see.

01:15:54.377 --> 01:15:55.447
Were you asked out?

01:15:56.077 --> 01:15:57.146
Were you asked out?

01:15:57.147 --> 01:15:59.577
Then we're happy.

01:15:59.847 --> 01:16:00.976
But doesn't that mean...

01:16:00.977 --> 01:16:03.047
- one person is left out? - Exactly.

01:16:03.647 --> 01:16:06.017
Can they not ask anyone out?

01:16:06.517 --> 01:16:09.257
- It looks like it. - Really?

01:16:10.127 --> 01:16:12.257
I put it inside.

01:16:13.057 --> 01:16:17.167
(Si Woo seems troubled at the mention of Hee Dong.)

01:16:17.527 --> 01:16:18.797
I was concerned.

01:16:19.497 --> 01:16:20.667
I was concerned about him.

01:16:20.997 --> 01:16:24.437
I even thought, "Did he not ask anyone out on purpose?"

01:16:24.607 --> 01:16:27.236
He may be laid-back,

01:16:27.237 --> 01:16:29.247
but this is an important moment.

01:16:30.007 --> 01:16:34.576
I don't think he would've...

01:16:34.577 --> 01:16:36.317
just done nothing.

01:16:36.687 --> 01:16:38.217
"Why didn't he ask someone out?"

01:16:38.417 --> 01:16:40.417
"Is he alone? Will he stay here alone?"

01:16:41.017 --> 01:16:42.556
"What will he do when he's alone?"

01:16:42.557 --> 01:16:44.757
I kept thinking about it.

01:16:45.757 --> 01:16:50.227
(Si Woo actually wanted Hee Dong to ask her out.)

01:16:54.367 --> 01:16:55.707
What will I do?

01:16:56.437 --> 01:17:00.277
You didn't ask the new person out, right?

01:17:00.907 --> 01:17:02.346
- No. - Then you'll probably go...

01:17:02.347 --> 01:17:03.747
on a date with the new person.

01:17:04.377 --> 01:17:06.177
- Someone new is joining? - A latecomer.

01:17:06.847 --> 01:17:08.687
- Someone new is joining? - There's someone new?

01:17:09.917 --> 01:17:11.287
The book.

01:17:11.347 --> 01:17:12.587
I'll go use it.

01:17:17.857 --> 01:17:20.297
(He opens the gift box again.)

01:17:21.997 --> 01:17:25.297
(There's another piece of information.)

01:17:26.137 --> 01:17:30.766
(A picture of a woman's back view)

01:17:30.767 --> 01:17:32.476
(There's a new woman resident. If you want to ask her out...)

01:17:32.477 --> 01:17:34.136
(on a date, write a letter on the back of the picture...)

01:17:34.137 --> 01:17:35.506
(and put it in the postbox in front of the door.)

01:17:35.507 --> 01:17:37.577
In the gift box...

01:17:37.677 --> 01:17:40.076
is the information about the new woman resident,

01:17:40.077 --> 01:17:41.117
only known to men.

01:17:41.987 --> 01:17:45.116
- I see. - The daughters don't know about it.

01:17:45.117 --> 01:17:47.286
- This is why he was so relaxed. - Then was Hee Dong...

01:17:47.287 --> 01:17:48.886
waiting for this on purpose?

01:17:48.887 --> 01:17:50.186
He could've been.

01:17:50.187 --> 01:17:51.926
He has something to fall back on.

01:17:51.927 --> 01:17:53.256
I guess so.

01:17:53.257 --> 01:17:55.696
He's not the type to think that far.

01:17:55.697 --> 01:17:56.726
Is he not?

01:17:56.727 --> 01:17:58.296
He doesn't think that far.

01:17:58.297 --> 01:17:59.836
- Is that a picture? - It's a picture.

01:17:59.837 --> 01:18:01.266
- It's her picture. - Her picture?

01:18:01.267 --> 01:18:03.007
- Really? - Yes.

01:18:03.137 --> 01:18:04.836
- She has long hair. - She has long hair.

01:18:04.837 --> 01:18:07.007
She appears to be a strong female latecomer.

01:18:07.407 --> 01:18:08.747
I think she draws.

01:18:08.977 --> 01:18:10.576
(Making the parents with daughters nervous)

01:18:10.577 --> 01:18:11.877
Maybe she majors in arts.

01:18:13.847 --> 01:18:18.787
(All four sons received her picture.)

01:18:20.117 --> 01:18:21.556
(Did you consider the new resident...)

01:18:21.557 --> 01:18:23.426
(when you requested a date?)

01:18:23.427 --> 01:18:25.157
I wasn't torn.

01:18:25.697 --> 01:18:29.497
I was interested in Yu Bin the most.

01:18:30.497 --> 01:18:31.736
- Cool. - Cool.

01:18:31.737 --> 01:18:32.797
He's certain.

01:18:35.737 --> 01:18:37.167
When I saw it,

01:18:37.367 --> 01:18:41.546
all I thought about was asking Si Woo to go on a date.

01:18:41.547 --> 01:18:43.607
It didn't really impress me.

01:18:44.747 --> 01:18:47.617
Men are firm.

01:18:48.287 --> 01:18:49.916
First of all,

01:18:49.917 --> 01:18:53.117
I don't tend to step forward.

01:18:53.387 --> 01:18:57.426
I'm not certain about whom to choose yet.

01:18:57.427 --> 01:19:01.227
When I saw the new resident's picture,

01:19:01.527 --> 01:19:03.696
I thought she'd be okay.

01:19:03.697 --> 01:19:05.096
(She'd be okay.)

01:19:05.097 --> 01:19:08.437
Since I'm new, and so is she,

01:19:08.637 --> 01:19:11.307
I thought we might get along.

01:19:11.577 --> 01:19:14.177
- Now it makes sense. - Right.

01:19:15.907 --> 01:19:18.577
(Requesting a date to the new woman)

01:19:19.577 --> 01:19:23.587
(Writing his greeting carefully)

01:19:25.217 --> 01:19:28.757
(How did Hee Dong greet her?)

01:19:36.827 --> 01:19:42.337
(One is bothered.)

01:19:43.137 --> 01:19:47.077
(While the other is excited.)

01:19:54.317 --> 01:19:59.987
(Excited to send the postcard)

01:20:01.317 --> 01:20:03.486
(What is the new woman like?)

01:20:03.487 --> 01:20:05.227
Si Woo expects...

01:20:05.427 --> 01:20:07.697
Hee Dong to be left alone.

01:20:07.827 --> 01:20:09.396
- She's not expecting him... - Right.

01:20:09.397 --> 01:20:10.796
- to see the new resident. - Right.

01:20:10.797 --> 01:20:12.767
- Women don't know about her. - No.

01:20:13.567 --> 01:20:14.897
Things are getting odd.

01:20:15.437 --> 01:20:17.036
What if the new resident...

01:20:17.037 --> 01:20:18.606
gets along with Hee Dong?

01:20:18.607 --> 01:20:21.436
- Then Si Woo will feel betrayed. - Then...

01:20:21.437 --> 01:20:23.546
- This is getting... - She'll be annoyed.

01:20:23.547 --> 01:20:25.847
This is getting dangerous.

01:20:27.947 --> 01:20:32.157
(Meanwhile, the new resident...)

01:20:33.587 --> 01:20:37.727
(received Hee Dong's postcard.)

01:20:39.657 --> 01:20:41.696
(Hello. Let's hang out together today.)

01:20:41.697 --> 01:20:42.926
- "Hello." - "Let's hang out together today."

01:20:42.927 --> 01:20:44.196
